Name: A-10
Abstract: A-10 has an earthy, hashy taste that provides a very heavy body stone.  Used to treat insomnia and chronic pain.

Name: A-Train
Abstract: A-train is a hybrid between afghani Mazar I Sharif and the clone-only Arcata e-32 Trainwreck

Name: Acapulco Gold
Abstract: One of the most well-known strains, Acapulco Gold comes to us from the areas in and around Acapulco, Mexico. Orange hairs both light and dark are present, resembling a gold nugget.

Name: Afghan Big Bud
Abstract: Afghan Big Bud has the best of both parents, Afghan Kush and Big Bud with it's Afghan taste and Big Bud shape.

Name: Afghan Diesel
Abstract: With it's citrus smell and taste, Afghan Diesel is described as tasting light and sweet.

Name: Afghan Kush
Abstract: Originating from the Hindu Kush mountains of Afghanistan, Afghan Kush is very potent indica.  High THC level makes it great to heal whatever ails you.

Name: Afghani
Abstract: Afghani will provide the user with a very strong, almost narcotic, physical high.  Useful for treating insomnia and chronic pain.

Name: Afghanica
Abstract: A 65/35 indica/sativa hybrid that grows well in temperate regions.

Name: Afghooey
Abstract: Afghooey is a nice potent and satisfying strain.  Soaring, potent and very very narcotic, the qualities and traits place Afghooey in the top tier of quality cannabis.

Name: Afgoo
Abstract: Afgoo is an indica-dominant strain that has a sweet and piney scent.

Name: Afwreck
Abstract: Afwreck is a hybrid cross of Afghani and Trainwreck.  Strong sativa effects with immediate head-concentrated high.

Name: Agent Orange
Abstract: An orange-smelling strain that has a citrus aftertaste.  Uplifting and almost trippy high can be experienced from this strain of cannabis.

Name: AK-47
Abstract: A great afghani kush cannabis strain that is mostly sativa but has all the good indica body stone characteristics.  Good for many medicinal uses but overdoing it will leave you glued to the couch.

Name: AK-48
Abstract: AK-48 is an indica-dominant hybrid cannabis strain but the high leans definitely towards the sativa side of the spectrum.  AK-48 is known for dense buds and fast flowering with an exceptional aroma.

Name: Alaskan Thunder Fuck
Abstract: A strong sativa strain, Alaskan Thunder Fuck will have you feeling the effects soon after exhale.  Originates in the Manatuska Valley area in Alaska.

Name: Alien Dawg
Abstract: With a sour and punget odor, Alien Dawg has a light, bitter taste and presents a brilliant mind/body high.

Name: Alien OG
Abstract: Alien OG is a strain cross from Tahoe OG and Alien Kush.

Name: Allen Wrench
Abstract: A popular strain for sativa-lovers, Allen Wrench presents the best qualities of it's parents, Trainwreck and New York City Diesel with crisp flavors of sour fruit. It's aroma has been characterized as sour, and flowery, leaving a fruity after-scent.

Name: Alohaberry
Abstract: Originating from the tropical islands of Hawaii, Alohaberry releases an aroma and taste of tropical berries.

Name: Ambrosia
Abstract: With a sweet tropical flavor and dense sticky buds, Ambrosia's high will hit you quick and throughout your body.

Name: Amethyst
Abstract: Amethyst is a cross of Lavender and Afghani Hawaiian with deep purple color.  Strong and pungent smell with a relaxing high.

Name: Amnesia Haze
Abstract: A mostly sativa hybrid, Amnesia Haze won first prize a the Hightimes Cannabis Cup in '04.  Sativa looks, aroma, and high.

Name: Arjan's Strawberry Haze
Abstract: Strawberry Haze is characterized by it's strawberry smell and sweet taste. It has a THC level up to 20% and CBD level of approximately 1.2%.

Name: Atomic Northern Lights
Abstract: With an three-time Cannabis Cup winning parent, Atomic Northern Lights will leave you feeling a mind/body high with uplifting effects.

Name: Avalon
Abstract: A selectively bred cross between Afghani and Blueberry.  Avalon has strong sedating effects with a hashy taste.

Name: Banana Diesel
Abstract: This lavender and blueberry aroma-filled strain has it's lineage from Blue Berry and White Widow.

Name: Banana Kush
Abstract: Banana Kush has a slight but pleasant banana scent and flavor.  This indica provides a very nice, strong full body stone.

Name: Banana Og
Abstract: Banana OG is a cross between OG Kush and Banana.

Name: Belladonna
Abstract: Belladonna is a mostly sativa strain that also carries good indica characteristics making for a very nice hybrid.

Name: Big Bud
Abstract: Big Bud is a favorite among indoor marijuana growers because of its unmatched yield.  Large buds with large leaves.  Stock with more expensive varieties if you really want to get a good high.

Name: Big Budda Cheese
Abstract: The Big Buddha Cheese is a very unique plant and until now was available as clone form only. Originating in the U.K, this 15 year old variety has been the leading dominant strain in the history of the underground British Indoor cannabis scene.

Name: Big Wreck
Abstract: Indica-dominant hybrid will slow down time but leave your reflexes in tact.

Name: Black Domina
Abstract: Black Domina blends the world's finest indica genetics into a rapid-flowering, crystal-coated hybrid.

Name: Black Jack
Abstract: Black Jack produces hard buds with huge, grape-like calyxes that are completely encrusted with THC! The smoke is heavy and flavoursome, and produces an exceptionally long-lasting high.

Name: Black Widow
Abstract: An evenly balanced hybrid strain, Black Widow is the sister of White Widow and maintains the families reputation for high natural THC levels.

Name: Blue Cheese
Abstract: The blue cheese medical cannabis strain is a hybrid cross between blue berry and UK Cheese.  A smooth high with euphoric and psychedelic effects.

Name: Blue Dragon
Abstract: Blue Dragon is usually so dark purple that it looks black.  This weed has aromatic hints of fruity pebbles and grapes.

Name: Blue Dream
Abstract: Ideal for pain management, Blue Dream combines the body high of an indica with the cerebral sativa effects.

Name: Blueberry
Abstract: Blueberry gets its name from the fruity smell and sweet blueberry taste when smoked.  This weed provides a pleasant and very long lasting high, a favorite among seasoned smokers.

Name: Blueberry Cheesecake
Abstract: Child of Blueberry and Big Buddha Cheese, Blueberry Cheesecake smells very much like it's name.

Name: Blueberry Haze
Abstract: A cross between blueberry and haze.  Provides a happy and euphoric high when properly moderated.

Name: Blueberry Headband
Abstract: Blueberry crossed with Headband, this hybrid has a sweet blueberry taste and smell.

Name: Bubba Kush
Abstract: A pure indica, Bubba Kush provides and intense and relaxing high.

Name: Bubba OG
Abstract: Great for relaxing, hanging out, and just enjoying life.

Name: Bubble Gum
Abstract: Sweet and fruity smell and taste, truly resembling bubble gum.  Provides a euphoric high and has won four awards in the High Times Cannabis Cup.

Name: Bubbleberry
Abstract: Bubbleberry has a pungent skunky smell but smoke is smooth with a nice fruity taste.

Name: Buddha's Sister
Abstract: Buddha's sister has a flavor like a tart cherry candy, and the scent is tart rather than sweet. The high is creative and cerebral in its effects.

Name: California Orange
Abstract: California Orange has a pronounced citrus aroma and flavor.  A 50/50 hybrid that produces very sticky and dense buds

Name: Candy Jack
Abstract: Candy Jack was the second place sativa winner at the first ever High Times Cannabis Cup in the U.S.

Name: Cannadential
Abstract: Grows like Cannalope, tastes like LA Confidential. This plant is the perfect mix of indica/sativa. Heavy buds and a fruity smell brought to us by those crazy geneticists from DNA Genetics.

Name: Cannalope Haze
Abstract: Sweet smelling buds with a melon taste, Cannalope Haze produces a high that will hit you in the temples and eyes.

Name: Cannatonic
Abstract: Cannatonic is a hybrid cross with an MK Ultra mother and G13 Haze father.  Cannatonic has been known to have a nearly 1:1 ratio of THC & CBD.

Name: Caramelicious
Abstract: Caramelicious is a hybrid cannabis variety that has sticky buds and a caramel flavor.  A favorite after dinner smoke for some, provides a sweet taste and happy high.

Name: Casey Jones
Abstract: Casey Jones is coming down the track.  Sugary sweet with subtle hints of citrus.  Casey was a famous engineer with a famous train wreck

Name: Cat Piss
Abstract: With a name like Cat Piss, this strain is actually quite sweet and sour tasting.

Name: Cataract Kush
Abstract: This is the combination of LA Confidential and OG Kush. This strain was created by DNA Genetics and it has blankets of crystals and looks almost grayish-black.

Name: Champagne Kush
Abstract: Known as a "luxurious strain," Champagne Kush smells and has a flavor similar to champagne.

Name: Cheese
Abstract: One of the most potent and considered best all-around strains, Cheese has a THC content up to 20%.

Name: Cheese Quake
Abstract: Cheese Quake by TGA Subcool Seeds is a cross of Cheese and Querkle.

Name: Chemdawg
Abstract: Chemdawg is a good hybrid marijuana strain.  It has a long list of medicinal uses and provides a nice mellow high when being smoked or vaporized.

Name: Chemdawg 4
Abstract: This indica-dominant strain smells of Pinesol and tastes of lemon.

Name: Chernobyl
Abstract: Rated in the Top 10 Strains by High Times, Chernobyl creates a long-lasting cerebral high with a unique lime-sherbet smell.

Name: Cherry Ak-47
Abstract: A cherry phenotype of Ak-47, Cherry AK-47 has a THC level up to 16% with a cherry flavor and taste.

Name: Cherry Kush
Abstract: Cherry and Kush, two great tastes that taste great together.  You won't be disappointed with this strain.

Name: Cherry Pie
Abstract: Cherry Pie smells and tastes just like a cherry pie. Has a high that comes on in minutes and sticks around for a couple of hours.

Name: Chiesel
Abstract: Cheese and NYC Diesel come together to form the Chiesel cannabis variety.  Strong smell is to be expected considering its lineage, provides a euphoric and functional stone.

Name: Chocolate Chunk
Abstract: Chocolate Chunk by TH Seeds is a pure indica that will meld you with the couch.

Name: Chocolate Kush
Abstract: With an aroma of vanilla and chocolate, this strains famous parents brings on a cerebral and heavy high.

Name: Chocolope
Abstract: Chocolope is a cross between OG Chocolate Thai & Cannalope Haze Cannabis varieties.  This strain smells minty with a bit of sweetness.

Name: Church OG
Abstract: From Gods Gift and OG Kush, Church OG provides a strong body high with a THC level up to 19%.

Name: Cinderella 99
Abstract: A cannabis sativa dominant strain that is popular among many long term weed smokers.  A good all around variety that us nice when hanging out with friends or just relaxing at home.

Name: Connie Chung
Abstract: The parents of this strain speak for themselves...the classic LA flavor crossed with the old school G13 Haze.

Name: Cotton Candy Kush
Abstract: A nice indica that has an unmistakable cotton candy taste to it.

Name: Cracker Jack
Abstract: Cracker Jack is a sativa strain that crosses Jack Herer with Green Crack.

Name: Crimea Blue
Abstract: Crimea Blue is a hybrid strain bred by Barney's Farm that is a cross between Blueberry and Crimean hash plant.

Name: Critical Mass
Abstract: Named after it's "critical mass" of production, this strain yields buds with a THC level of 19-22%.

Name: Death Star
Abstract: Sour Diesel cross with Sensi Star.

Name: Deep Purple
Abstract: Deep Purple provides great grape taste and a calming and relaxing high.

Name: Diablo
Abstract: Diablo has a THC content up to 20% with a short flowering time. Stems from Blueberry, Grapefruit and South African Sativa.

Name: DJ Short Blueberry
Abstract: This Blueberry is a dense and stout plant with red, purple and blue hues.

Name: Dopium
Abstract: Dopium, a cross between ChemDawg and Sour Diesel has a unique scent while keeping elements of that classic Sour Diesel smell.

Name: Dream Queen
Abstract: Smelling of bubblegum and pineapple, Dream Queen takes on the best of her parents, Blue Dream and Space Queen.

Name: Durban Poison
Abstract: One of the most coveted sativa strains for its mind-blowing effects.  Durban Poison is sure to impress the most jaded pot smokers.

Name: Dutch Dragon
Abstract: Dutch Dragon is a sativa variety bred by Paradise Seeds.

Name: Dutch Hawaiian
Abstract: Dutch Hawaiian provides a good body high and is lime green in color.

Name: Dutch Treat
Abstract: Smelling of sweet pine and citrus, Dutch Treat has a THC of up to 18% with a taste of eucalyptus.

Name: Dynamite
Abstract: Dynamite is a short and bushy Indica that provides high yield and high quality bud.

Name: Ed Rosenthal Super Bud
Abstract: A superb balance of the best traits from each end of the cannabis spectrum has been achieved through expert selection over countless generations.

Name: Edelweiss
Abstract: The Edelweiss strain gets its namesake from the white flower that grows high in the Swiss Alps.

Name: Exodus Cheese
Abstract: Unusual cheesy smell with deeply pungent earthy taste.  Uplifting high that lasts about four hours.

Name: Fire OG
Abstract: THC up to 20% and the appearance of nuggets that are on fire, Fire OG is one of the strongest of the OG strains.

Name: Flo
Abstract: Creating a "flo" of buds to harvest, Flo was rated #1 in 1996 at the Cannabis Cup.

Name: Fruity Pebbles
Abstract: A fluffy light green strain covered in crystals and plenty of orange trichomes.  Slightly fruity tasting, this weed provides a nice hybrid high.

Name: Fucking Incredible
Abstract: Fucking Incredible is a pure Indica and was created by combining the genetics of two magnificent Inidcas back in 1990

Name: G-13
Abstract: G-13 is a cannabis strain of legends.  A very strong variety of indica that is a favorite of anybody who tries it. G13 marijuana will give you a very heavy indica body high.

Name: G13 Haze
Abstract: Original G13 crossed with an original Haze to give you a more uplifting high while still retaining the heavy-hitting indica undertones.

Name: Girl Scout Cookies
Abstract: A popular San Francisco strain, Girl Scout Cookies tastes of cotton candy and has a THC level of 18-23%.

Name: God Bud
Abstract: A great strain for small spaces, God Bud doesn't grow much higher than 3 feet tall.

Name: God's Gift
Abstract: A popular California strain, God's Gift tastes of citrus, grape and hash with a very strong THC content up to 22%.

Name: Golden Goat
Abstract: Created by accident in Kansas, Golden Goat has a high that lasts up to 2 hours with a sweet, sour and spicy taste.

Name: Granddaddy Purple
Abstract: Grand daddy purple is a cannabis indica strain that originates from purple Ukrel and Big Bud.  Has a grape smell and taste when smoked and provides more energy than a typical indica strain.

Name: Grape Ape
Abstract: A good all-around indica strain that will help with your pain or nausea.

Name: Grape God
Abstract: Grape God is a cross between Godbud and Grapefruit.  Produces large yields and high levels of THC.

Name: Grape Kush
Abstract: Grape Kush provides a euphoric head high along with a nice body stone.

Name: Grapefruit
Abstract: Grapefruit has the sweet soft smell of grapefruit with a sweet taste and nice tropical high.

Name: Grapefruit Haze
Abstract: A beautiful blend of fruity and spicy flavours with a very cerebral high.

Name: Grapefruit Kush
Abstract: Large buds with a fruity hash taste, Grapefruit Kush produces enjoyable smooth and creamy smoke with a great high.

Name: Green Candy
Abstract: Green Crack and Candy Kush cross, Green Candy provides a cerebral head high and relaxing body stone.

Name: Green Crack
Abstract: Green Crack is a mostly sativa strain that provides a short cerebral high, sometimes described as 'spacey'.

Name: Green Dream
Abstract: Green Dream is a sativa-dominant hybrid cross of Green Crack and Blue Dream.

Name: Green Queen
Abstract: From Green Crack and Space Queen, this gold and yellow strain has a THC up to 17%.

Name: Gumbo
Abstract: Getting its name from the classic bubble gum flavor, Gumbo is a perfect medicine for the evenings and has a smooth taste and finish.

Name: Harlequin
Abstract: Harlequin typically has very high levels of CBD making it good for pain relief and a favorite among medical users.

Name: Hash Plant
Abstract: The current Hash Plant variety available from Sensi Seeds is a cross between an original hash plant and Northern Lights #1.  Named for its hashy taste, hash plant has been a parent to many of the great Sensi Seeds hybrid strains.

Name: Hashberry
Abstract: Hashberry has a classic indica flavor with hashish undertones. It's thick stems are necessary to support the heavy buds, providing a classic aroma and flavor of mint or pepper.

Name: Hashplant Haze
Abstract: The uplifting high of the Hashplant Haze is enjoyable throughout the day due to it's being a sativa dominant strain

Name: Hawaiian Delight
Abstract: Hawaiian Delight has a strong and musky aroma, hashy finish with a pleasant after taste.

Name: Hawaiian Punch
Abstract: Originating in Hawaii, Hawaiian Punch delivers a "punch" not unlike the most righteous wave in Hawaii. This strain is extremely potent, yet delivers an aloha feeling to your mind and body, much like an ocean breeze.

Name: Hawaiian Snow
Abstract: Hawaiian Snow is a cross of Hawaiian Haze, Pure Haze and Neville's Haze.  This sativa marijuana has a complex taste and provides radiant highs.

Name: Haze
Abstract: The Haze variety of cannabis sativa is very potent and high in THC content.  Great for medicinal uses or social settings.

Name: Headband
Abstract: Headband is a combination of OG Kush, Master Kush, and Sour Diesel.  It smokes smooth and pleasant while providing pain and stress relief.

Name: Hempstar
Abstract: Hempstar is a three way cross between Skunk, Oasis, and Haze. Bred by Dutch Passion Seeds.

Name: Herojuana
Abstract: Herojuana is a great indica with very strong flavor.  Provides great relief for chronic pain sufferers.

Name: Himalayan Gold
Abstract: Spawn from the Himalayan mountains, this plant has been known to grow up to 8 feet tall and smells of chocolate.

Name: Hindu Kush
Abstract: Hindu Kush will provide you with a calm, active mental state different than that of other Indicas.

Name: Hindu Skunk
Abstract: Hindu Skunk is a cross of Hindu Kush and Skunk #1.  Provides a smooth smoke and a strong mellow high.

Name: Hog's Breath
Abstract: 2002 Cannabis Cup winner Hog's Breath is bred by legendary Hindu Kush and Afghani and provides an overall mind and body high.

Name: Hollands Hope
Abstract: Outdoor growers love Hollands Hope for its ability to produce great weed even during a wet summer.  Full indica that provides a very heavy stone.

Name: Ice
Abstract: Ice is a 50/50 hybrid with a powerful and heavy stone that will leave you feeling lazy for hours.

Name: Ice Cream
Abstract: This indica-dominant 60/40 strain bred by Paradise Seeds is a strain that creates a great hybrid balance.

Name: Jack Flash
Abstract: Jack Flash is an offshoot of the legendary Jack Herer strain mixed with Skunk and Haze.  A very powerful indica-dominant strain with a pungent skunky smell.

Name: Jack Frost
Abstract: Developed over 5 years with ancestors such as Jack Herrer, White Widow, Northern Lights #5 and Rainbow Kashmiri, Jack Frost has a THC content up to 22.5%.

Name: Jack Herer
Abstract: Jack Herer is named after the late hemp proponent and activist.  This strain is well known for its strong cerebral and body high.

Name: Jack the Ripper
Abstract: Jack the Ripper is well named because it is absolutely killer weed.

Name: Jamaican Pearl
Abstract: Sweet tropical taste and a breezy Jamaican high make this sativa a favorite of any experienced smoker.  Smoking Jamaican Pearl brings a taste of the tropical beach to your living room.

Name: Jillybean
Abstract: Jillybean was rated as one of the top 10 strains in 2007 by High times and has tangy orange and mango flavors. THC has been measured up to 17%.

Name: Juicy Fruit
Abstract: Also known as Fruity Juice, this cannabis strain has a THC content up to 15-20% and tastes similar to fruit punch.

Name: Kaboom
Abstract: A cross of Jacks Cleaner and Vortex, this sativa-dominant strain gives you a speedy high that is also good for pain relief.

Name: Kahuna
Abstract: Kahuna is a 4-way cross that brings together a wide set of influences for a complex high.

Name: Kali Mist
Abstract: A favorite strain among expert marijuana users.  Kali Mist provides a great sativa high that relieves pain and symptoms of PMS.

Name: Kandy Kush
Abstract: OG Kush crossed with Trainwreck, Kandy Kush won the first ever Western Slope Cannabis Crown in Aspen.

Name: King Kush
Abstract: With it's lineage from OG Kush and Grape Ape, King Kush contains flavors of citrus, pine and kush. This strain comes across as sweet and sour with it's powerful and tangy grape scent, and some hints of lavender.

Name: Kosher Kush
Abstract: Kosher Kush is the first commercial strain to be blessed by a Rabbi.

Name: Kryptonite
Abstract: With a THC content up to 25%, Kryptonite is capable of sending users into a deep indica medicated state.

Name: Kushberry
Abstract: This is the perfect blend of two West Coast flavors, Blueberry from Oregon and the OG Kush from LA.

Name: LA Confidential
Abstract: LA Confidential cannabis is a hugely popular strain.  Smooth and piney taste with a classic skunky aroma.

Name: LA OG
Abstract: LA OG is very potent variety of medical cannabis. An earthy taste with a powerful head and body high.

Name: LA Woman
Abstract: The taste is sweet and robust with the flavor lasting well after the exhale.

Name: Lamb's Bread
Abstract: Bright green and sticky, Lamb's Bread gives you energy and positive introspection.  Good stress reliever and helpful for depression sufferers.

Name: Lavender
Abstract: Lavender brings together a world of weed.  A mashup of strains that span the globe from Afghanistan, Hawaii, Korea, the U.S., and Europe.

Name: Lavender Kush
Abstract: With its ancestry from all around the world, Lavender Kush has a THC content up to 18% and is renowned for its potency and flavor.

Name: Lemon Diesel
Abstract: Reigning in as one of the Top Ten in the 2010 Emerald Cup, Lemon Diesel smells and tastes like citrus and pepper with a high that can "sneak up" on its user.

Name: Lemon Haze
Abstract: Lemon Haze smells of lemon peels and appears yellow due to its amber hairs. THC content is about 15-20%.

Name: Lemon Kush
Abstract: Lemon Kush is a sativa-dominant hybrid that is good for daytime use.  Has intense lemon flavor and scent.

Name: Lemon Skunk
Abstract: Lemon Skunk Cannabis is a cross hatch between two Skunks with phenotypes chosen for their zesty lemon characteristics.

Name: LSD
Abstract: Known for it's psychedelic qualities, LSD cannabis strain has a THC level up to 24% and does well in most growing conditions.

Name: M-39
Abstract: M-39 is a cannabis strain with a fast flowering time and a THC content up to 16.5%, when it is grown and harvested properly.

Name: Malawi
Abstract: Malawi is a pure sativa strain that comes from the Salima region of Malawi in southeast Africa.

Name: Mango
Abstract: Since the 1960s, Mango cannabis strain has been around, and was improved in 1991 when crossed with KC33. Tasting and smelling of the mango fruit, this strain has a THC content up to 20%.

Name: Mango Kush
Abstract: Tasting and smelling like a mango, the Mango Kush marijuana strain is covered with orange pistils and can grow up to 5 feet tall.

Name: Maple Leaf Indica
Abstract: The taste of Maple Leaf Indica is sweet and citrusy.  This strain has been known to act as an aphrodisiac and gives off a very relaxing and sensational body buzz.

Name: Martian Mean Green
Abstract: A combination of Sharksbreath and G13 Haze.  One of DNA Genetics' flagship strains, super pungent aroma and consciousness  altering high.

Name: Master Kush
Abstract: Master Kush provides a pleasing and relaxing body buzz but not overly sleepy.

Name: Maui Waui
Abstract: This Hawaiian legend will give you energy and inspiration.  The soaring sativa high will make you feel as happy as if you were relaxing on a tropical beach.

Name: Mazar I Sharif
Abstract: Grown in the far north of Afghanistan, Mazar-i-Sharif has a spicy and earthy taste that produces a very good up high.

Name: Mendocino Purps
Abstract: Also known as Mendo Purps or The Purps, this marijuana strain was a Top Ten winner in 2007 with High Times Strains of the Year.

Name: Mexican Sativa
Abstract: The thought of Mexican marijuana often reminds us of the cheap weed that we smoked in high school.  This strain is a bred masterfully to bring out all the best sativa effects that you would expect from more expensive seeds.

Name: Millennium
Abstract: Named after the idea that it will be around for many years, millennium is a balanced hybrid with 75% indica from the mountains of Iran crossed 25 percent with a Niagara/Shiva sativa. Easy to grow indoors and outdoors.

Name: MK Ultra
Abstract: A very strong variety of cannabis indica.  Named after mind control experiments done by the government, this strain will definitely control your mind.

Name: Morning Star
Abstract: Morning Star has as much as 24% THC content, provides an uplifting and mind-expanding high.

Name: Mr. Nice
Abstract: Mr. Nice is named in honor of Howard Marks who was one of the biggest marijuana smugglers of our time.  This indica-dominant cannabis strain has extremely dense buds with a sweet smell.  An easy smoke that provides a strong and very mellow high.

Name: Nebula
Abstract: Nebula is an award winning cannabis strain with a psychedelic buzz and honey filled smell and taste.

Name: Neville's Haze
Abstract: Neville's Haze won the Cannabis Cup in 1998 and has a THC content up to 21%.

Name: Northern Lights
Abstract: The Northern Lights genetics are part of many of the most promising indoor strain varieties.  One of the most potent and famous cannabis strains in the world she delivers a stoned body high like no other.

Name: Northern Lights #5
Abstract: Northern Lights #5 is in the popular Northern Lights family of cannabis strains.  Introduced in 1989 it has since won many awards at the Cannabis Cup and other harvest festivals.

Name: NYC Diesel
Abstract: NYC Diesel is a great sativa-dominant strain for use during the day.  Go out or stay in, this strain will not disappoint.

Name: OG Diesel Kush
Abstract: OG Diesel Kush has a THC content up to 19.6% with dark green buds and milky trichromes.

Name: OG Kush
Abstract: OG Kush is a very popular strain.  This variety put Southern California on the map for marijuana growers everywhere.  Mostly sativa so it is not technically a Kush strain.

Name: Ogre
Abstract: Ogre has a pungent and lemony scent and provides a strong body high.

Name: Orange Bud
Abstract: A combination of two pure Skunk family members, Orange Bud is a marijuana strain that is easy to grow with a THC level up to 16.5%.

Name: Orange Crush
Abstract: Bred with Californian Ornage and Blueberry, Orange Crush has a THC content up to 15% and a powerful cerebral high lasting up to 2 hours.

Name: Orange Dream
Abstract: A sativa-dominant cross of Orange Crush and Blue Dream.

Name: Orange Kush
Abstract: With a strong tangy citrus flavor, Orange Kush has a THC content up to 20%.

Name: Orange Velvet
Abstract: Orange Velvet taste and smells remarkably like orange dreamsicles.  The high gives a euphoric lift while maintaining focus and clarity.

Name: Outer Space
Abstract: Outer Space is a sativa-dominant strain that is a cross of Island Sweet Skunk and Trinity and is known for cerebral and creative effects. It has a citrusy odor that is strong and produces a flavorful smoke. Great as a daytime medicine.

Name: Pandora's Box
Abstract: A mostly sativa cross of Jack the Ripper and Space Queen, this strain has high THC levels and a citrus flavor.

Name: Permafrost
Abstract: Permafrost marijuana strain has the parents of Trainwreck and White Widow and has a "frost" of crystals on the buds.

Name: Pineapple
Abstract: Smelling and resembling a pineapple, this marijuana strain has a flowering time of 7-8 weeks.

Name: Pineapple Express
Abstract: Pineapple Express has a THC content up to 17% and smells like apple and mango, with a taste of pineapple.

Name: Pineapple Kush
Abstract: Pineapple Kush has a THC content up to 15% and tastes of sweet pineapple.

Name: Platinum Kush
Abstract: With a silver/platinum shade due to its many crystals, Platinum Kush creates a strong buzz affecting both the head and body.

Name: Pot of Gold
Abstract: Pot of Gold is covered in resin and can be very sticky.  Hash and fruity taste when smoked, very quick to grab hold of your brain.

Name: Power Kush
Abstract: A popular strain in Amsterdam, Power Kush has a THC content up to 16% and smells of strawberry and orange.

Name: Purple Afghani
Abstract: This Afghani is a mostly Indica inbred to produce thick and heavy buds. This variety has dark green leaves and calyxes that turn purple at flowering. Medium-high leaf to flower ratio with a subtle aroma and a very good high.

Name: Purple Buddha
Abstract: Purple Buddha combines grape flavors of the Purps with the creamy berry tastes of Blue Buddha.

Name: Purple Haze
Abstract: Purple Haze is a great strain for medicinal users because it provides strong relief from pain.

Name: Purple Mr. Nice
Abstract: GDP and Mr. Nice come together in this very heavy indica, do not operate heavy machinery after smoking.

Name: Purple Trainwreck
Abstract: Lemon-scented cross between GDP and Trainwreck.  Gives a slight body high, nicely euphoric and uplifting.

Name: Purple Urkle
Abstract: The legendary purple urkle is a very popular indica strain.  It possesses an interesting sweet grape flavor when smoked.  Gives you a nice strong stone, light-weights beware.

Name: Q3
Abstract: A sativa dominant strain.

Name: Qleaner
Abstract: Qleaner is a mostly sativa strain that provides an impressive high to even the most jaded pot snob.

Name: Querkle
Abstract: Purple Urkle crossed with Space Queen produces this indica/staiva 80/20 marijuana variety.  Querkle has a fruity grape & berry scent.

Name: Rainbow
Abstract: Tastes like tropical Starburst with purple, orange and green colored buds. THC range of 17-22%.

Name: Raskal OG
Abstract: Bred by Cali Connection, this indica-based hybrid smells of lemon and pine and has a THC level up to 17%.

Name: Recon
Abstract: The ReCon is a perfect blend of two parts LA Confidential and one part Cannadential.

Name: Richie Rich
Abstract: Richie Rich is a Northern Lights #5 crossed with Skunk #1.  It is a favorite among medical users for pain relief.

Name: Rocklock
Abstract: Rocklock marijuana is a cross between the RockStar and Warlock cannabis strains.

Name: Romping Goddess
Abstract: Romping Goddess is an original creation that combines a powerful, local medicinal strain with the Cannabis Cup winning "God Bud".

Name: Romulan
Abstract: Romulan is a very strong indica that provides good relief from pain but will definitely have you stuck to the couch.

Name: Romulan Grapefruit
Abstract: Top quality hybrid, amazingly strong scent. Grows like the Grapefruit in size and stature but has a bigger punch and stronger smell due to the Romulan influence

Name: SAGE
Abstract: S.A.G.E. is a well-balanced Haze cross with a robust indica strain.  Spicy sandalwood flavor combined with a long lasting and uplifting high make this the plant for those who like the best.

Name: Sage N Sour
Abstract: THSeeds crossed their legendary S.A.G.E. strain with an equally powerful Sour Diesel to create Sage N Sour.

Name: Seattle Blue
Abstract: Seattle Blue has a sweet and fruity taste that provides a strong and euphoric body high.  A great indica for relaxing.

Name: Sensi Star
Abstract: Sensi Star is a very strong indica with THC levels reaching up to 20%.

Name: Shaman
Abstract: Shaman is a sativa strain that is helpful in treating anxiety, depression, and chronic pain.  Provides a euphoric head high and strong body high.

Name: Shark Shock
Abstract: Shark Shock is a cross of the famous White Widow and Skunk #1 strains.  This indica is also sometimes referred to as Peacemaker or Great White Shark.

Name: Shiva Skunk
Abstract: An amazing cross between NL#5 and SK#1, one of the most potent indica-dominant strains available.  Strong and mellow high with no bad after effects.

Name: Silver Haze
Abstract: A strong sativa-dominant hybrid, the Silver Haze buzz is strong and clear.  A good choice for day time smoking.

Name: Skunk #1
Abstract: Skunk #1 is a cross of Afghani, Mexican Acapulco Gold and Columbian Gold genetics.  Bred by Dutch Passion since 1978.

Name: Skunky Diesel
Abstract: A cross of Sensi Skunk with NYC Diesel.  Skunky Diesel comes on fast and strong.

Name: Skydog
Abstract: Skydog is notorious for being a pretty intense strain that takes tokers to new heights.

Name: Snow White
Abstract: Early and abundant resin production is attributed to her White Widow mother.

Name: Snowcap
Abstract: Snow Cap is a pure cannabis sativa that will provide you with a pure sativa high.  Expect lots of giggles during a funny movie, also ideal for going out to a party with lots of friends.

Name: Sour Diesel
Abstract: Sour Diesel mairjuana provides a fast-acting, dream high.

Name: Sour Flower
Abstract: Sour Flower is a sativa that provides relief from pain and anxiety.

Name: Sour OG
Abstract: Sour OG is a cross of Sour Diesel and OG Kush.  A very nice weed to smoke, not overly powerful but provides a relaxing yet energetic high.

Name: Space Queen
Abstract: A cross of Romulan and Cinderella 99, very fruity taste and head high.

Name: Strawberry Cough
Abstract: This sativa-dominant strain will tickle your throat and make you cough like no other.  Good for a lift of spirits or going out and enjoying the great outdoors.  Can provide a pretty powerful high, be careful with the uninitiated.

Name: Strawberry Dream
Abstract: Strawberry Dream is a cross of Blue Dream and Strawberry Cough.  A 60/40 sativa-dominant hybrid strain that is very potent and sweet smelling.

Name: Super Cat Piss
Abstract: The Super Cat Piss strain smells just like you would imagine.  The name doesn't provoke very appetizing ideas but this is a great sativa.

Name: Super Lemon Haze
Abstract: Super Lemon Haze, from Greenhouse Seeds, a cross between Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze. This strain has a lemon smell and a sweet taste.

Name: Super Silver Haze
Abstract: A great sativa-dominant cannabis strain that has won many honors and the High Times Cannabis Cup.  Gives a great energetic body high.

Name: Super Skunk
Abstract: Skunk lovers rejoice, Super Skunk was bred specifically for you.  The strong skunky smell provides a very pleasant high to all who try it.

Name: Sweet Island Skunk
Abstract: 19.6% THC, Sweet Island Skunk is a sativa-dominant hybrid grown on Vancouver Island.

Name: Sweet Tooth
Abstract: A perfect pairing of indica and sativa high with a very sweet taste.

Name: Thai-Tanic
Abstract: A very compact Sativa-dominant variety, classic chocolate Thai smell and taste.

Name: The Flav
Abstract: The Flav was included in the Hightimes top 10 of 2008, a cross between Romulan and Space Queen.

Name: The Void
Abstract: The Void is a cross between Apollo-13 and Querkle strains. It tastes like grape saltwater taffy while providing a motivational high.

Name: The White
Abstract: The White strain looks like it has been rolled in powdered sugar when done flowering.  This strain is a mostly indica hybrid.

Name: Trainwreck
Abstract: Trainwreck will creep up on you and leave you feeling like a freight train crashed into your face.  Sativa-dominant hybrid that is renowned for pain relief and other medicinal uses.

Name: Trinity
Abstract: A rumored hard to find strain, Trinity is known to have a strong skunk-like smell with an uplifting high.

Name: Tropicali
Abstract: One of the newer hybrids, Tropicali is known for providing an uplifting and cerebral high with a frosty mint green color.

Name: Violator Kush
Abstract: Known for it's high THC and CBD levels, Violator Kush is a mostly indica cross of Hindu Kush and Malana.

Name: Vortex
Abstract: Vortex won first place for best sativa in the 2010 Cannabis Cup.

Name: Warlock
Abstract: Warlock is an indica-dominant strain but also has some obvious sativa characteristics.  Sweet and fruity smell and provides a mellow high.

Name: White Berry
Abstract: White Berry provides a sativa head high when lightly smoked and a nice body stone when smoked in higher quantities.

Name: White Dawg
Abstract: From the lineage The White and Chem Dawg.

Name: White Rhino
Abstract: White Rhino is a hybrid cross of White Widow and an unknown indica strain.  Great for medicinal use because it has a high THC content.

Name: White Russian
Abstract: White Russian may be the strongest plant known currently.  With 22% THC it has won multiple Cannabis Cups and will not disappoint with its strong cerebral high.

Name: White Widow
Abstract: White Widow is an extremely popular new hybrid marijuana strain.  Known for its potent high and frequent rap song references.  The buds are covered in crystals giving it the look of powdered sugar.

Name: Wonka's Bubbilicious
Abstract: Wonka's Bubbilicious has a taste reminiscent of Bubblicious bubble gum from your childhood. Taste is known to subtly change flavors and tones over the period of two minutes, similar to Wonka's candy, thus the name.

Name: Yumboldt
Abstract: Yumboldt is known to leave the user with heavy eyelids and a smile.
